Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.52,0:01:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\an8\2c&HC08000&\3c&H804000&\4c&HC08000&\b1\be1}戦場の太陽は高く揺れて　感情に棲み着く陰を落とす
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.52,0:01:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnDFLiHei-Md\2c&HC08000&\3c&H804000&\4c&HC08000&\b1\be1}戰場上的艷陽高高搖曳著　照射著棲住於感情深處的陰影
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.52,0:01:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\an8\2c&HC08000&\3c&H804000&\4c&HC08000&\b1\be1}知らないまま　痛みに変わること　悟るように
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.52,0:01:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnDFLiHei-Md\2c&HC08000&\3c&H804000&\4c&HC08000&\b1\be1}我明白著　它會在不知不覺中　讓一切變得痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.52,0:02:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\an8\2c&HC08000&\3c&HFF8080&\4c&HC08080&\b1\be1}悲しみから生まれた夢も　世界と君が許してくれる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.52,0:02:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnDFLiHei-Md\2c&HC08000&\3c&HFF8080&\4c&HC08080&\b1\be1}即使是從悲傷中誕生的夢　也會得到世界與你的諒解
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.52,0:02:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\an8\2c&HC08000&\3c&HFF8080&\4c&HC08080&\b1\be1}そう　瞼の裏で繰り返す　この空が呼ぶ声に
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.52,0:02:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnDFLiHei-Md\2c&HC08000&\3c&HFF8080&\4c&HC08080&\b1\be1}一切　就在眼前不斷重複著　在這天空下的呼喚聲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.52,0:02:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\an8\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC080FF&\4c&H8080FF&\b1\be1}響いて　ただ駆け抜けた　胸に眩い衝動
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.52,0:02:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnDFLiHei-Md\2c&HC08080&\3c&HFF80FF&\4c&H8080FF&\b1\be1}響徹著　一心只想著讓懷裡耀眼的衝動飛奔而去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.52,0:02:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\an8\2c&HC08080&\3c&HFF80FF&\4c&H8080FF&\b1\be1}弾けた想いに　My star will shine forever
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.52,0:02:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnDFLiHei-Md\2c&HC08080&\3c&HFF80FF&\4c&H8080FF&\b1\be1}在爆發的情感裡　My star will shine forever
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.52,0:02:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\an8\2c&HFFFF80&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HC08080&\b1\be1}あの日抱えた全て　強く生きて行け　僕の中で今
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.52,0:02:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnDFLiHei-Md\2c&HFFFF80&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HC08080&\b1\be1}而我內心現在　緊緊抱著那天的一切　堅強地活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.52,0:02:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\an8\2c&HC08000&\3c&H804000&\4c&HFF8080&\b1\be1}蘇る　時間　この場所で　僕ら絶対譲れない願いを
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.52,0:02:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnDFLiHei-Md\2c&HC08000&\3c&H804000&\4c&HFF8080&\b1\be1}讓停滯的時間復甦　這個地方　是我絕對不能退讓的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.52,0:02:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\an8\2c&H0080FF&\3c&H4080FF&\4c&H00FFFF&\b1\be1}ただ一つこの声で　強く刻んで行け　This is The Asterisk War
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.52,0:02:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnDFLiHei-Md\2c&H0080FF&\3c&H4080FF&\4c&H00FFFF&\b1\be1}用這一聲的吶喊　深深地刻劃下　This is The Asterisk War
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.62,0:00:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.62,0:00:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.62,0:00:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.62,0:00:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.62,0:00:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}古斯塔夫·馬爾洛?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.26,0:00:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}聽說昨晚的犯人是一名國際通緝的罪犯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.30,0:00:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}他是曾在六芒星
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.98,0:00:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}引發「翡翠黃昏」這一恐怖襲擊案的團伙的成員
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.06,0:00:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}這麼說是恐怖分子嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.46,0:00:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}不 他似乎是出於金錢目的才參與到「翡翠黃昏」當中的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.69,0:00:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}我想這次的襲擊 他應該也沒有政治上的目的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.34,0:00:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}聽他當時的語氣 似乎也是受人所托
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.22,0:00:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}估計他背後應該存在一個龐大的組織吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.58,0:00:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}不過 為什麼會有人提出那種要求呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.46,0:00:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}警方那邊提出了增派護衛人員的要求 你們意下如何?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.50,0:00:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}我就不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.90,0:00:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}我也不用
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.50,0:00:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}看樣子大家都不需要呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.57,0:00:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}明白了 我會轉告他們的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.98,0:01:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}那麼 我還有些事情要調查 就先失陪了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.42,0:01:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}如果沒事了的話 那我們也...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.02,0:01:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}等一下 尤莉絲
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.42,0:01:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}你和天霧君先留一下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.54,0:01:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}我昨天不是說過有要緊事要和你們談談嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.55,0:02:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}那麼 你究竟要找我們談什麼事?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.27,0:03:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}有兩件事情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.62,0:03:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}天霧君
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.30,0:03:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.51,0:03:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}你能和尤莉絲結婚嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.19,0:03:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}你突然說什麼啊 皇兄
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.59,0:03:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}開玩笑也該有個分寸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.51,0:03:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}嘛 總之先從訂婚開始好了 你覺得如何?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.26,0:03:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}不...不是 你可能有所誤會了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.67,0:03:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}我和尤莉絲並不是那種關係
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.27,0:03:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}沒...沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.23,0:03:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}你們之間的關係我已經從芙羅拉那裏聽說了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.35,0:03:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}但是沒有關係嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.03,0:03:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}現如今 這都不是什麼大問題
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.15,0:03:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}怎麼不是大問題
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.39,0:03:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}我說這些可都是為了你好啊 尤莉絲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.75,0:03:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}這樣下去 你遲早...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.79,0:03:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}多管閒事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.66,0:03:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}什麼意思?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.11,0:03:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}就是說如果置之不理的話 那尤莉絲也會像我一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.79,0:03:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}被統合企業財體指定一個對他們有利的配偶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.23,0:04:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}所以還不如趁現在 好歹先挑選一個自己中意的物件
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.79,0:04:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}你並不討厭天霧君對吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.09,0:04:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}這...當然不討厭...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.23,0:04:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}難道你昨天讓我們參加凱旋遊行是為了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.07,0:04:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}嗯 想讓他稍微露個臉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.63,0:04:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}可...可是 為什麼這麼突然
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.75,0:04:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}以前這方面的事情我不是全都拒絕掉了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.07,0:04:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}情況變了啊 尤莉絲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.95,0:04:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}因為你獲得了「鳳凰星武祭」的冠軍啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.79,0:04:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}以前統合企業財體也沒有當真
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.82,0:04:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}但是 這次的奪冠讓你的價值一下子提升了許多
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.67,0:04:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}這... 這個...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.11,0:04:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}不過 現在你仍然能夠搶先下手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.75,0:04:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}他是和你一同參加「鳳凰星武祭」的搭檔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.11,0:04:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}這一點是最名正言順的了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.79,0:04:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}你意下如何 天霧君
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.71,0:05:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}這個國家小歸小 但應該也不至於讓你覺得不便
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.74,0:05:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}我覺得這個提議並不壞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.91,0:05:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}確實沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.55,0:05:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}不過 相應地也會伴隨有某些束縛 沒錯吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.83,0:05:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}人只要活在世界上 就不可能擁有完全的自由哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.34,0:05:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}多多少少的束縛總是免不了的 我認為只能選擇接受
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.95,0:05:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}可是要接受什麼樣的束縛 應該還是有選擇的餘地才對
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.51,0:05:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}尤莉絲她就是為了打破這樣的枷鎖 才會來到六芒星的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.23,0:05:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}而我 絕不能成為尤莉絲的枷鎖
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.63,0:05:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}你還真是正直得超乎我想像啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.51,0:05:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}明白了 明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.43,0:05:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}這個話題就到此打住吧
