Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.95,0:05:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.39,0:05:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}假設尤莉絲自身希望你成為她的枷鎖 你願不願意接受呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.63,0:06:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}皇兄 你在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.31,0:06:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}這個...得到了那個時候才會明白...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.91,0:06:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}原來如此 看來還是存在可能性的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.51,0:06:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}如果你沒事了的話 那我們就先告辭了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.67,0:06:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}走了 綾斗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.87,0:06:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}等一下 我剛才不是說有兩件事的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.90,0:06:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}要是你再敢說無聊的事情 我可不饒你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.55,0:06:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}這件事很快就能說完
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.66,0:06:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}尤莉絲 你能不能別去參加「獅鷲星武祭」?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.15,0:06:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}你這話是認真的嗎 皇兄
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.79,0:06:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}當然是認真的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.19,0:06:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}理由呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.63,0:06:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}在凱旋遊行上你也看到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.22,0:06:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}你現在的人氣非常驚人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.11,0:06:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}如果繼續這樣下去 我的立場就有可能不保
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.19,0:06:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}所以我希望你不要去參加「獅鷲星武祭」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.27,0:06:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}我拒絕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.04,0:06:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}傷腦筋了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.72,0:06:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}難道你剛才的話 真的是認真的嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.64,0:07:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}當然是認真的 是我由衷的請求啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.20,0:07:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}我能成為這個國家的國王
