Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.80,0:07:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}如果尤莉絲奪得「獅鷲星武祭」的冠軍
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.44,0:07:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}獲得了比我更大的影響力的話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.32,0:07:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}那他們就有可能把尤莉絲推上王座
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.12,0:07:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}她應該抱持著為了窮人改變這個國家的念頭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.63,0:07:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}但這個國家是受統合企業財體支配的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.00,0:07:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}尤莉絲只會陷入痛苦罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.56,0:07:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}好了 天霧君 我再問你一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.92,0:07:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}你能替我設法說服尤莉絲嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.48,0:07:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}我辦不到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.08,0:07:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}這樣嗎 我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.67,0:07:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}哎 沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.16,0:07:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}那我就更賣力地扮演好傻瓜的角色吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.20,0:07:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}尤莉絲應該在湖對岸的孤兒院裏
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.99,0:08:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}從小開始 一旦發生點什麼 她一定會跑去那裏
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.59,0:08:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}不好意思 她就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.92,0:08:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}沒錯
