Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.24,0:08:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}放馬過來吧 隨你們從哪裏攻
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.28,0:08:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}挺厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.16,0:08:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}喂 很危險的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.76,0:08:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}是天霧綾斗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.88,0:08:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}真的耶
