Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.80,0:09:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}是皇兄告訴你的嗎?
