Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.28,0:09:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}特蕾莎修女
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.44,0:09:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}歡迎你 天霧綾斗先生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.44,0:09:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}我是特蕾莎 負責打理這個教會和孤兒院
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.91,0:09:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}歡迎回來 尤莉絲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.40,0:09:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}「鳳凰星武祭」我看了 挺厲害的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.76,0:09:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}嘛 那當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.68,0:09:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}還真敢說
