Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.16,0:09:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}好久不見 尤莉絲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.60,0:09:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}時間流逝得真快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.00,0:09:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}那個尤莉絲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.40,0:09:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}不知不覺間都已經成為一位那麼出色的王女殿下了
