Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.44,0:09:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}總讓人覺得不太對勁就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.12,0:09:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.84,0:09:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.52,0:09:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}幸好尤莉絲選擇的是像你這樣的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.40,0:09:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}不 我這種人...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.28,0:09:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}不必謙虛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.72,0:09:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}從你看向尤莉絲的眼神中就能看得出來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.04,0:10:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}好了好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.24,0:10:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}到此為止 快回去工作吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.12,0:10:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}是
