Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.76,0:10:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}再見咯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.72,0:10:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.52,0:10:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}芙羅拉的事情給你添麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.83,0:10:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}我在這裏再次向你致謝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.76,0:10:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}不會 而且實際上救出芙羅拉的人也不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.60,0:10:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}總之先由你作為代表接受大家的謝意吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.16,0:10:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}不客氣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.28,0:10:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}這裏似乎有好幾位修女都是「星脈世代」呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.56,0:10:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}包含我在內有四個人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.20,0:10:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}特蕾莎修女 相當於是我身為「魔女」的啟蒙師父
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.72,0:10:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}現在我也一直在教孩子們防身術
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.48,0:10:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}那是...溫室嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.72,0:11:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}是以前在這裏待過的一個女孩喜歡的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.04,0:11:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}她不擅長和別人爭
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.63,0:11:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}真的是一個很善良的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.24,0:11:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}我去外面透透氣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.88,0:11:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}尤莉絲?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.56,0:11:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}不...不好意思 先失陪一會
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.84,0:11:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}看來果然還是不行呢
