Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.56,0:11:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}我當然明白
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.72,0:11:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}我很清楚皇兄重視我甚於一切
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.04,0:11:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}也明白我究竟是多麼地受上天眷顧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.63,0:11:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}正因為這樣 我無法容忍這個國家現在的模樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.71,0:11:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}我覺得尤莉絲一直在努力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.16,0:12:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}那家孤兒院不也不用再為金錢操心了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.52,0:12:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}確實 鳳凰星武祭奪冠之後
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.16,0:12:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}拯救那家孤兒院的目標成功實現了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.16,0:12:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}但終究是杯水車薪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.00,0:12:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}就結果來說 這個世界的體系本身
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.56,0:12:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}依然會不斷產生出類似這條貧民街一樣的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.20,0:12:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}不斷產生出孤兒院 以及只能依托那裏生存的孩子們
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.28,0:12:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}至少 我希望能讓這個國家從這種詛咒中解脫出來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.64,0:12:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}這就是你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.27,0:12:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}下一次「獅鷲星武祭」的奪冠願望嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.14,0:12:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}剛才難道是...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.02,0:13:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}尤莉絲?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.98,0:13:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}不 肯定沒錯 那的確是...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.29,0:13:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}等等 尤莉絲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.78,0:13:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}你突然間怎麼了啊 尤莉絲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.78,0:13:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}土壤都腐蝕了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.38,0:13:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}好久不見了啊 奧菲莉亞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.26,0:13:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}你說奧菲莉亞 難道她是...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.38,0:13:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}為什麼要來?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.78,0:14:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}差不多有一年沒見了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.89,0:14:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}想不到竟然會在這種地方再見到你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.53,0:14:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}我已經再三提醒過你 不要再和我有任何瓜葛了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.78,0:14:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}我的請求還是和一年前一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.18,0:14:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}回來吧 奧菲莉亞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.86,0:14:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}那裏不是你應該 待的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.26,0:14:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}別說了 尤莉絲 我只有遵從我的命運
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.06,0:14:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}你是無法顛覆我的命運的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.62,0:14:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}我不認同
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.78,0:14:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}我如今的命運就在這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.90,0:14:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}如果你無論如何都想讓我聽從你的話...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.94,0:14:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}我當然明白
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.57,0:14:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}不過 這次可不會再像一年前那樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.46,0:14:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}等...等一下 尤莉絲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.81,0:14:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}綾斗 你不准出手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.26,0:14:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}這是我和奧菲莉亞之間的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.62,0:14:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}尤莉絲...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.82,0:15:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}這次我一定要打碎你的校徽
