Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.98,0:15:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}那就是奧菲莉亞· 蘭朵露芬的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.54,0:15:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}啊 尤莉絲 沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.85,0:15:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}憑你的力量還是不行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.58,0:15:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}還沒完
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.73,0:15:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}華麗綻放吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.90,0:15:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}灼炎太陽華
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.98,0:15:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}我要來了 奧菲莉亞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.02,0:16:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}難道她...僅僅靠著星辰力在防禦?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.38,0:16:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.30,0:16:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}你的命運太過孱弱 所以我早就提醒過你了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.90,0:16:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}化為塵土
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.42,0:16:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}尤莉絲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.86,0:16:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}尤莉絲 尤莉絲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.86,0:17:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}這就是「孤毒魔女」的瘴氣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.98,0:17:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}你就是天霧綾斗?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.29,0:17:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}不是已經分出勝負了嗎 再打下去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.42,0:17:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}雖然很可悲 但命運一旦啟動 連我也無法停止
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.14,0:17:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}如果你不想被波及 還是趕快離開吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.70,0:17:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}抱歉 這我辦不到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.46,0:17:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}真遺憾
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.30,0:17:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}天霧辰明流 矢汰烏
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.80,0:17:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}啊 那就是「黑爐魔劍」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.64,0:17:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}老實說 完全沒有勝算啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.84,0:17:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}難道說!?
