Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.59,0:18:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}真是了不得啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.52,0:18:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.96,0:18:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}不過 我馬上就會讓你解脫的
