Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.84,0:18:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}其實有人委託我解決那兩個人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.40,0:18:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}每收拾一人就能獲得一定程度的成功報酬
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.76,0:18:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}要是可以的話 能不能將那兩個獵物讓給我呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.72,0:18:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}喂 奧菲莉亞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.64,0:18:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}你跑哪裏偷懶去了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.04,0:18:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}我不是再三囑咐你不要離開研究所的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.59,0:18:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}我馬上回去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.04,0:19:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}隨你便吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.84,0:19:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.20,0:19:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}等等
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.72,0:19:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}哎呀呀 真是讓人嚇出一身冷汗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.56,0:19:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}雖然已經聽到過傳聞 但想不到竟然會是那麼恐怖的怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.36,0:19:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}老天保佑 老天保佑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.28,0:19:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}好了 接下來我也該完成我的工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.24,0:19:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}向你們介紹一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.59,0:19:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}這是我的作品 歐特魯斯和凱魯貝洛斯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.96,0:19:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}如何? 這威猛的姿態和神話中描述的一模一樣吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.24,0:20:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}不妙了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.44,0:20:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}天霧辰明流劍術...初傳...
